message.text: Welcome to /Calculator by @Git Center! Give me any mathematical expression and I'll calculate it. The supported functions are: sin(x), cos(x), tan(x), log(x), log2(x), log10(x), floor(x), ceil(x), round(x). The supported values are: pi, e, rnd (a random number in [0; 1) ). The supported operators are: +, -, *, /, % (modulo), ** (power), &, |, ^ (bitwise and/or/xor, respectively).
